    "body": "## What's Changed\r\n* renaming simple to sample in readme by @ryhinchey in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/237\r\n* adding installation instructions to readme by @ryhinchey in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/233\r\n* chore: add support for OSSF scorecard reporting by @inigomarquinez in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/291\r\n* ci: replace travis with github actions by @inigomarquinez in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/290\r\n* docs: add example output for log formats by @jonchurch in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/299\r\n* ci: use ubuntu-latest by @bjohansebas in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/301\r\n* ci: apply OSSF Scorecard security best practices by @UlisesGascon in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/300\r\n* remove --bail by @jonchurch in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/314\r\n* ⬆️ bump on-headers by @ctcpip in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/319\r\n\r\n## New Contributors\r\n* @inigomarquinez made their first contribution in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/291\r\n* @jonchurch made their first contribution in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/299\r\n* @bjohansebas made their first contribution in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/301\r\n* @UlisesGascon made their first contribution in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/300\r\n* @ctcpip made their first contribution in https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/pull/319\r\n\r\n**Full Changelog**: https://github.com/expressjs/morgan/compare/1.10.0...1.10.1",
